Varek_king: So… this is what you’ve become.\
Cyber’s pet… leading the charge to finish what they started.
Player: We tried to talk. You turned away.
Varek_king: Because you brought ruin to our home!
Varek_king: Cyber doesn’t want peace — they want a world of wires and silence.\
A kingdom where nothing breathes unless it’s programmed to.
Player: That’s not true. Cyber gives life where Magus let it die.\
While you ordered loyalty, your people starved in your name.
Varek_king: I was protecting them!
Nataly: By bleeding them dry?!
Nataly: You traded unity for grief. And now you want to drag us all down with you.
Varek_king: Enough words.\
If you stand for Cyber… then you stand against me.
